item.title: CVE-2021-24403|2024-08-03T19:28:23.817Z -- unknown -- wordpress%20page%20contact
item.description: The Orders functionality in the WordPress Page Contact plugin through 1.0 has an order_id parameter which is not sanitised, escaped or validated before inserting to a SQL statement, leading to SQL injection. The feature is available to low privilege users such as contributors
